{"name": "odoo-addon-l10n-br-fiscal-certificate", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-l10n-br-fiscal-certificate", "version": "16.0.1.0.1.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["erpbrasil.assinatura", "odoo-addon-l10n_br_fiscal", "odoo"], "summary": "A1 fiscal certificate management for Brazil", "upload_time": 1726629456}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Production%2FStable-green.png\n    :alt: Production/Stable\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fl10n--brazil-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/l10n-brazil\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/16.0/l10n_br_fiscal_certificate\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/l10n-brazil-16-0/l10n-brazil-16-0-l10n_br_fiscal_certificate\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/l10n-brazil&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-renatonlima: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/renatonlima.png?size=40px\n    :alt: renatonlima\n    :target: https://github.com/renatonlima\n    ```\n---\n\n# A1 fiscal certificate management for Brazil\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:5a9c76b45da87cbf58a0ef957347904bc879482356e5d6665d898b535bf346f8\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nPermite gerenciar seus certificados A1 para a assinar e transmitir seus\ndocumentos eletr\u00f4nicos.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAbra o menu Configura\u00e7\u00f5es>Empresas. Dentro da aba fiscal tem uma nova\np\u00e1gina \"certificados\" onde voc\u00ea pode fazer o upload dos certificados A1.\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 14.0.1.0.0 (2023)\n\nPrimeira vers\u00e3o do m\u00f3dulo: o c\u00f3digo vinha sendo desenvolvido desde a\nvers\u00e3o 8 mas estava integrado dentro m\u00f3dulo l10n_br_fiscal. O c\u00f3digo foi\nextra\u00eddo para deixar o m\u00f3dulo l10n_br_fiscal mais leve.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_br_fiscal_certificate%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Akretion](https://www.akretion.com/pt-BR):\n\n  - Renato Lima \\<<mailto:renato.lima@akretion.com.br>>\n  - Rapha\u00ebl Valyi \\<<mailto:raphael.valyi@akretion.com.br>>\n\n- [KMEE](https://www.kmee.com.br):\n\n  - Luis Felipe Mileo \\<<mailto:mileo@kmee.com.br>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-renatonlima }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-brazil](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/16.0/l10n_br_fiscal_certificate) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.certificate", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models..certificate", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models..res_config_settings", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.res_company", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2013  Renato Lima - Akretion", "Copyright (C) 2020  Luis Felipe Mileo - KMEE", "License AGPL-3 - See http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.res_company.ResCompany", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_certificate.models.res_company.ResCompany._compute_certificate", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}